{"tid":604411,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"善忘叫大方，記得叫小氣？","createTime":"2018-03-24T16:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T16:08:11.000Z","uid":113807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"094d4e7ba5b7aa9b14b60dcf842fa1acb818f74b","tid":604411,"uid":113807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T16:05:47.000Z","msg":"每次同女朋友鬧交 ，我會講佢曾經點樣對我點樣激嬲我，件事可能只係一兩日之前發生，當時我見大家個氣氛好似幾好，所以就當冇事，忍左。 但件事係發生左點可以當冇呢？佢係激嬲左我，我講返出黎，係因為我覺得個時機岩，係時候討論下。但點知佢話唔記得左，話我小氣，叫我大方d,個日完左就要當冇事。咁即係唔駛講，唔駛討論，唔駛改善啦..好啦 最後都係我認錯 大家當冇事..其實都有條刺 仲要佢根本冇反醒過 唔打算改 即係我講黎都冇用. 所以我都算 唔講 佢話點就點 但佢成日都話我小氣 開口埋口都話我小氣 即係定形左我 所以搞到好似係佢係度忍我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8151189ae23545353fd8880c3a79cf72785f4ca1","tid":604411,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T16:06:56.000Z","msg":"你鬧佢 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你連雞都不如</span></strong></span> 囉"},{"pid":"38f26fbd54c2562e422124406174c8db242fc7ee","tid":604411,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T16:08:11.000Z","msg":"你喺度呻乜9？飛佢啦"}]}